data.value: 1. Welcome online Voting System. 2. In case you are Voter there is "Menu" for you in sidebar named " Voter". 3. In case you are not already Registered As a Voter, Click on "Registered As Voter" to register yourself. 4. Enter all your the credentials correctly. 5. Set your password and never share it with anyone. 6. When you enter all the credentials Press "Submit" button. 7. In case your Data is successfully submitted a messege box will appear.If not you may Re-Enter your Data and try again. 8. After Applying for Registration, a confirmation message will be sent you on Phone No and Email either you are "Eligible" or ""Eleligible". 9. You can check your Registration under "Check Your Registration" button. 10. In case you are Registered Voter,and Eligible to cast Vote,Click "Vote" button in menu. 11. For vote casting you must remember your "CNIC ID" and "Password". 12. While Casting vote stay concious and handle things slowly and gently. 13. After submitting your Vote a confirmation messege will be displayed on screen.
